        </p>

        <h5>
            <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Atheists-Angry-Things-Godless-ebook/dp/B007MCMKV6">Why Are You Atheists So Angry? 99 Things That Piss Off the Godless</a>
        </h5>

        <p>
            <br>
        </p>

        <p>
            <span>​Is it because they're selfish, joyless, lacking in meaning, and alienated from God? Or is it because they have legitimate reasons to be angry -- and are ready to do something about it? Armed with passionate outrage, absurdist humor, and calm intelligence, popular blogger Greta Christina makes a powerful case for outspoken atheist activism, and explains the empathy and justice that drive it.</span>
        </p>

